text:
https://about.pinterest.com/en/terms-service

*10. Arbitration* 

“For any dispute you have with Pinterest, you agree to first contact us 
<https://help.pinterest.com/login-request> and attempt to resolve the 
dispute with us informally…


if not…


Each party will be responsible for paying any AAA filing, administrative 
and arbitrator fees in accordance with AAA rules, except that Pinterest 
will pay for your reasonable filing, administrative, and arbitrator fees if 
your claim for damages does not exceed $75,000 and is non-frivolous (as 
measured by the standards set forth in Federal Rule of Civil Procedure 
11(b)).”
